       shortened by Stefan Allan, 23-Feb-2006.) $)
    sylcom $p |- ( ph -> ( ps -> th ) ) $=
      ( wi a2i syl ) ABCGBDGEBCDFHI $.
  $}

  ${
    syl5com.1 $e |- ( ph -> ps ) $.
    syl5com.2 $e |- ( ch -> ( ps -> th ) ) $.
    $( Syllogism inference with commuted antecedents.  (Contributed by NM,
