  $( Commutative law for equivalence.  Theorem *4.21 of [WhiteheadRussell]
     p. 117.  (Contributed by NM, 5-Aug-1993.)  (Revised by NM,
     11-Nov-2012.) $)
  bicom $p |- ( ( ph <-> ps ) <-> ( ps <-> ph ) ) $=
    ( wb bicom1 impbii ) ABCBACABDBADE $.

  ${
    bicomd.1 $e |- ( ph -> ( ps <-> ch ) ) $.
