  ${
    3bitr4g.1 $e |- ( ph -> ( ps <-> ch ) ) $.
    3bitr4g.2 $e |- ( th <-> ps ) $.
    3bitr4g.3 $e |- ( ta <-> ch ) $.
    $( More general version of ~ 3bitr4i .  Useful for converting definitions
