  axi12 $p |- ( A. z z = x \/ ( A. z z = y \/
                 A. z ( x = y -> A. z x = y ) ) ) $=
    ( cv wceq wal wi wo ax-bnd sp orim2i ax-mp ) CDZADZECFZMBDZECFZNP
    EZRCFGCFZAFZHZHOQSHZHABCIUAUBOTSQSAJKKL $.

  $( Commutation law for identical variable specifiers.  The antecedent and
