  ${
    $d x ph $.
    $( Axiom to quantify a variable over a formula in which it does not occur.
       Axiom C5 in [Megill] p. 444 (p. 11 of the preprint).  Also appears as
       Axiom B6 (p. 75) of system S2 of [Tarski] p. 77 and Axiom C5-1 of
