     "flatten" the structure on the right side (whose tree structure is
     something like (wi (wceq (cv vx) (cv vy)) wph) ) into just (wcdeq vx vy
     wph).  (Contributed by Mario Carneiro, 11-Aug-2016.) $)
  df-cdeq $a |- ( CondEq ( x = y -> ph ) <-> ( x = y -> ph ) ) $.

